Scripts extraídos do arquivo SCRIPT.PAK com LuckSystem

=========================================
Luca System Tools
=========================================

* Planetarian SG

UNPACK SCRIPT:
./LuckSystem script decompile -s SCRIPT.PAK -c UTF-8 -O data/PlanetarianSG.txt -p data/PlanetarianSG.py -o planetarian

REPACK SCRIPT:
./LuckSystem script import -s SCRIPT.PAK -c UTF-8 -O data/PlanetarianSG.txt -p data/PlanetarianSG.py -i /sysroot/home/brocolis/Jogos/LuckSystem/planetarian -o /sysroot/home/brocolis/Jogos/LuckSystem/planetarian/export/SCRIPT.PAK


UNPACK PAK:
./LuckSystem pak extract -s BGCG.PAK -i BGCG.PAK -o planetarian/BGCG.PAK -a planetarian


CONVERTER CZ4 PARA PNG:
czutil decode arquivo.cz4 arquivo.png

CONVERTER PNG PARA CZ4:
czutil replace LOAD_BG.cz1 LOAD_BG.png LOAD_BG_NEW.cz1
